  "notes": [
    "Some formations include plus transport in their core units. When stated the following rules apply. 1) The formation may be dropped via dreadclaws from a purchased Space Ship at no additional cost. 2) It may take sufficent Chaos Rhinos to transport it once other upgrades with transports have been purchased. 3) When Land Raiders are available the following process should be followed. Purchase up to the max allowed Land Raiders. Add the minimum number of Rhinos to transport the remainder of the formation as per the plus transport option"
